\id 2TH
\h Tɛsɑlonikɑ II
\mt1 TIRERU YIRUSE TE PƆLU
\mt1 U TƐSALONIKAGIBU KUA
\ip Pɔlu u Tɛsɑlonikɑɡibu tireru yiruse teni yoruɑ domi u nuɑ mɑ ɡɑbɑ burisinɛ ben suunu sɔɔ Yesun wurɑmɑrun sɔ̃. Gɑbɑ tɑmɑɑ Yesun wurɑmɑ te, tɑ turuku kuɑ. Yerɑ bɑ ben sɔmburu deri. Bɑ ǹ mɑɑ ɡɑru mɔ̀ mɑ mɛro bisibu ɡɑbu bɑ sere bu nɔɔrimɔ. Gɑbɑ mɑɑ burisinɛ yèn sɔ̃ bɑ tɑmɑɑ Yesu u wurɑmɑ kɔ, mɑ u bu deri, mɑ n sɑ̃ɑre nɔni swɑ̃ɑ te bɑ wɑ Yesun sɔ̃ tɑ kuɑ kɑm. Yen sɔ̃nɑ Pɔlu u bu sɔ̃ɔsiru wɛ̃ te tɑ ɡerumɔ mɛ Yesun wurɑmɑru tɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑ. Mɑ u ɡɑru koo sɑri be ɡerusi bu kɑ sɔmburu ko. Mɛyɑ u mɑɑ be bɑ nɔni sɔ̃ɔmɔ dɑm kɑ̃ bu kɑ tɛmɑnɑ. Domi Yesu u koo bɑɑwure siriɑwɑ dee dee u sere nùn win ɑre wɛ̃.
\is1 Tire ten kpunɑɑ
\iq1 1. Tɔbiribu kɑ nuku yɛmiɑsiɑbu, wiru 1.
\iq1 2. Kɔ̃sɑn kowon kurɑmɑru kɑ Yesun wurɑmɑru, wiru 2:1-12.
\iq1 3. Kirɔbɑ, wiru 2:13n di sere wiru 3:15.
\iq1 4. Tɔbiri dɑ̃ɑkibu, wiru 3:16-18.
\c 1
\s1 Tɔbiribu
\p 
\v 1 Bɛɛ Yesun yiɡbɛruɡibu, bɛɛ be i wɑ̃ɑ Tɛsɑlonikɑɔ bɛɛ be i sɑ̃ɑ Gusunɔ bɛsɛn Bɑɑbɑ kɑ Yinni Yesu Kirisiɡibu bɛsɛ Pɔlu kɑ Silɑsi kɑ Timɔte, sɑ bɛɛ tɔburɑ.
\v 2 Gusunɔ Bɑɑbɑ kɑ Yinni Yesu Kirisi bu bɛɛ durom kuɑ kpɑ bu bɛɛ ɑlɑfiɑ kɛ̃.
\s1 Siribu ko n wɑ̃ɑ
\s2 Kirisin nɑɑrun tɔ̃ru sɔɔ
\p 
\v 3 Bɛsɛɡibu, n weenɛ sɑ n Gusunɔ siɑrɑmɔ sɑɑ bɑɑyere bɛɛn sɔ̃. N wɑ̃ sɑ n mɔ̀ mɛ yèn sɔ̃ bɛɛn nɑɑnɛ dokebu bu sosimɔ ɡem ɡem, mɑ kĩi te i mɔ bɛɛn tii tiinɛ sɔɔ tɑ mɑɑ kpɛ̃ɑmɔ tɑ sosimɔ.
\v 4 Yen sɔ̃nɑ bɛsɛn tii sɑ Yesun yiɡbɛnu woo kɑnɛ bɛɛn sɔ̃, domi i tɛmɑnɑ i yɔ̃ nɑɑnɛ dokebu sɔɔ nɔni swɑ̃ɑru kɑ tɔ̃yɑn sɑɑ.
\p 
\v 5 Yeniwɑ yɑ sɔ̃ɔsimɔ kɑm kɑm mɑ Gusunɔ u rɑ siri dee dee, kpɑ bu kɑ bɛɛ ɡɑrisi be bɑ turɑ bɑ n kɑ wɑ̃ɑ mi Gusunɔ u bɑndu swĩi tèn sɔ̃ i wɑhɑlɑ wɑɑmɔ.
\v 6 Domi Gusunɔ u koo ko ye n sɑ̃ɑ dee dee, u koo bu nɔni sɔ̃ be bɑ bɛɛ nɔni sɔ̃ɔmɔ.
\v 7 Mɑ bɛɛ be i nɔni swɑ̃ɑru wɑɑmɔ, u koo bɛɛ wɛ̃rɑbu wɛ̃ kɑ mɑɑ bɛsɛn tii, sɑnɑm mɛ Yinni Yesu koo kurɑmɑ wɔllun di kɑ dɔ̃ɔ yɑri kɑ win ɡɔrɑdo dɑmɡibu.
\v 8 Yesu wiyɑ u koo bu sɛɛyɑsiɑ be bɑ kun Gusunɔ yɛ̃, kɑ be bɑ kun wi, Yinni Yesun Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑ wure.
\v 9 Ben dii kɔsiɑru tɑ ko n sɑ̃ɑwɑ kɑm koo bi bu kun nɔru mɔ sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑ. Bɑ ko n kɑrɑnɛwɑ kɑ Yinni kɑ mɑɑ win yiiko dɑmɡiɑ,
\v 10 sɑnɑm mɛ u koo nɑ kpɑ win bɛɛrɛ yu sɔ̃ɔsirɑ wiɡibu sɔɔ, kpɑ nɑɑnɛ dokeobu kpuro bɑ n nùn kɑ̃sɑ tɔ̃ɔ te sɔɔ. Bɛɛn tii i ko n mɑɑ wɑ̃ɑ mi, domi i bɛsɛn seedɑ nɑɑnɛ doke ye sɑ di.
\p 
\v 11 Yen sɔ̃nɑ sɑ kɑnɑru mɔ̀ bɑɑdommɑ bɛɛn sɔ̃, Gusunɔ bɛsɛn Yinni u kɑ kpĩ u bɛɛn kookoosu siɑrɑ wɑ̃ɑ te u bɛɛ sokuɑ sɔɔ kpɑ win dɑm mu de i ɡeɑ ko ye i ɡɔ̃ru doke kpɑ mu mɑɑ de bɛɛn nɑɑnɛ dokebun kookoosu su n yibɑ.
\v 12 Nɡe mɛyɑ bɛsɛn Yinni Yesun yĩsirɑ koo kɑ bɛɛrɛ wɑ bɛɛn min di, kpɑ bɛɛ i mɑɑ bɛɛrɛ wɑ win min di Gusunɔ kɑ Yinni Yesu Kirisin durom sɑɑbu.
\c 2
\s1 Kɔ̃sɑn kowo
\p 
\v 1-2 Nɛɡibu, nɑ bɛɛ kɑnɑmɔ i ku de bɛɛn lɑɑkɑri yu burisinɑ, bɛsɛn Yinni Yesu Kirisin wurɑmɑrun ɡɑrin sɔ̃ kɑ mɑɑ bɛsɛn mɛnnɑbu win mi, i ku mɑɑ de sɔmɔbun ɡɑri ɡɛɛ ǹ kun mɛ wɑɑsu ɡɑɑ ǹ kun mɛ tire te bɑ nɛɛ nɑ yoruɑ, yen ɡɑɑ yu bɛɛ biti ko yɑ̀ n ɡeruɑ mɑ Yinnin tɔ̃rɑ tunumɑ kɔ.
\v 3 I ku de bu bɛɛ nɔni wɔ̃ke bɑɑ fiiko. Yinnin tɔ̃ɔ te, tu sere nɑ tɔn dɑbirɑ koo Gusunɔ seesi, yen biru kɔ̃sɑn kowo wi, u koo kurɑmɑ wi u sɑ̃ɑ kɑm kooren bii.
\v 4 U koo tii suɑ n kpuro kere kpɑ u ye kpuro seesi ye bɑ sokumɔ Yinni kɑ ye bɑ sɑ̃ɑmɔ. U koo mɑm dɑ u sinɑ Gusunɔn sɑ̃ɑ yerɔ kpɑ u tii soku Gusunɔ.
\p 
\v 5 I ǹ yɑɑye mɑ nɑ bɛɛ yeni sɔ̃ɔwɑ sɑnɑm mɛ nɑ wɑ̃ɑ bɛɛn mi?
\v 6 Tɛ̃, i yɛ̃ sɑ̃ɑ sɑ̃ɑ ye yɑ nùn nɛnusi sere win sɑɑ yu kɑ turi.
\v 7 Domi kɔ̃sɑ yɑ sɔmburu mɔ̀ kɔ ɑsiri sɔɔ. Adɑmɑ wi u ɡinɑ ye yinɑsiɑmɔ u ko n ye yinɑsiɑmɔwɑ sere bɑ̀ n kɑ nùn doonɑ.
\v 8 Sɑɑ yerɑ kɔ̃sɑn kowo wi, u koo kurɑmɑ kpɑ Yinni Yesu u nùn wom wure u ɡo, kpɑ u nùn kpeerɑsiɑ kɑ win nɑɑrun yiiko.
\v 9 Kɔ̃sɑn kowo wi, u koo nɑ kɑ Setɑm dɑm, kpɑ u sɔm mɑɑmɑɑkiɡii bwese bwesekɑ ko ye yɑ sɑ̃ɑ weesuɡiɑ.
\v 10 U koo mɑɑ bu nɔni wɔ̃ke bu kɑ kom kɔ̃sum ko, be bɑ koo kɑm ko yèn sɔ̃ bɑ yinɑ bu ɡem kĩɑ mɛ mu koo bu fɑɑbɑ ko.
\v 11 Yenin sɔ̃nɑ Gusunɔ u koo de ɡɑ̃ɑ dɑmɡinu ɡɑnu nu bu torɑsiɑ bu kɑ weesu nɑɑnɛ ko.
\v 12 Nɡe mɛyɑ, be bɑ ǹ ɡem nɑɑnɛ doke mɑ bɑ kom kɔ̃sum kuɑ kɑ nuku dobu, bɑ koo tɑɑrɛ suɑ.
\s1 Bɑ bɛɛ ɡɔsɑ i kɑ fɑɑbɑ wɑ
\p 
\v 13 Nɛɡibu, bɛɛ be Yinni u kĩ, sɑ ǹ ko ko sɑ kun Gusunɔ siɑre bɛɛn sɔ̃ sɑɑ bɑɑyere. Domi Gusunɔ u bɛɛ ɡɔsɑ sɑɑ toren di i kɑ fɑɑbɑ wɑ kɑ Hunde Dɛɛron dɑm wi u bɛɛ kuɑ Gusunɔɡibu, kɑ mɑɑ bɛɛn nɑɑnɛ ye i mɔ ɡem sɔɔ.
\v 14 Yenin sɑɑbuwɑ Gusunɔ u bɛɛ sokɑ kɑ bɛsɛn Lɑbɑɑri ɡeɑn kpɑrɑbu, i n kɑ bɔnu mɔ bɛsɛn Yinni Yesu Kirisin yiiko sɔɔ.
\v 15 Ǹ n mɛn nɑ nɛɡibu, i yɔ̃ro dim dim i n sɔ̃ɔsi ni nɛni ni sɑ bɛɛ sɔ̃ɔsi nɔɔ kɑ nɔɔ kɑ mɑɑ tireru sɔɔ.
\p 
\v 16 Gusunɔ bɛsɛn Bɑɑbɑ wi u sun kĩɑ, mɑ win durom sɑɑbu u sun dɑm kɑ̃ mɛ mu kun nɔru mɔ kɑ mɑɑ yĩiyɔ ɡeebu, wi kɑ bɛsɛn Yinni Yesu Kirisin tii
\v 17 bu bɛɛn ɡɔ̃rusu dɑm kɛ̃, kpɑ bu bɛɛ tɑ̃sisiɑ i kɑ sɔm ɡeenu kɑ ɡɑri ɡee kpuro ko.
\c 3
\s1 I sun kɑnɑru kuo
\p 
\v 1 Ye n tie nɛɡibu, i sun kɑnɑru kuo kpɑ Yinnin ɡɑri yi wɑ yi kpɑrɑrɑ fuuku, kpɑ yi n yiiko mɔ nɡe mɛ yi kuɑ bɛɛn suunu sɔɔ.
\v 2 I mɑɑ kɑnɑru koowo kpɑ Gusunɔ u sun wɔrɑ tɔn kɔ̃so wiru sɑribɑn nɔmɑn di, domi n ǹ tɔmbu kpuro bɑ ɡɑri yi nɑɑnɛ dokemɔ.
\p 
\v 3 Adɑmɑ Yinni u sɑ̃ɑ bɔrɔkini. U koo bɛɛ tɑ̃sisiɑ kpɑ u bɛɛ kɔ̃su tɔn kɔ̃so win sɔ̃.
\v 4 Yinni u derɑ sɑ bɛɛ nɑɑnɛ sɑ̃ɑ. Sɑ yɛ̃ mɑ i mɔ̀ ye sɑ bɛɛ yiire, mɛyɑ i ko n mɑɑ mɔ̀ i n dɔɔ.
\p 
\v 5 Kpɑ Yinni u de bɛɛn bwisikunu nu n woo Gusunɔn kĩru ɡiɑ kɑ mɑɑ Kirisin tɛmɑnɑbu sɔɔ.
\s1 N weenɛ tɔnu u sɔmburu ko
\p 
\v 6 Nɛɡibu, kɑ Yinni Yesu Kirisin yĩsiru sɑ bɛɛ yiiremɔ, i nɑɑnɛ dokeo bɑɑwure ɡɔwo wi u sɑ̃ɑ ɡɑru koo sɑri mɑ u ǹ sɔ̃ɔsinu swĩi ni sɑ bɛɛ wɛ̃.
\v 7 Bɛɛn tii i yɛ̃ mɛ n weenɛ i bɛsɛn dɑɑ sɑɑri. Domi sɑ ǹ kue ɡɑru koo sɑribɑ bɛɛn suunu sɔɔ.
\v 8 Sɑ ǹ ɡoon dĩɑnu di sɑ kun nin ɡobi kɔsie, ɑdɑmɑ sɑ sɔm sɛ̃sɔɡiru kuɑ bururu kɑ yokɑ sere sɑ wɑsirɑ kpɑ su ku kɑ ko ɡoon sɔmunu.
\v 9 N ǹ mɔ sɑ ǹ yen yiiko mɔ, ɑdɑmɑ sɑ kĩwɑ bɛsɛn tii su bɛɛ kom ɡem sɔ̃ɔsi mɛ i ko sɑɑri.
\v 10 Sɑnɑm mɛ sɑ wɑ̃ɑ bɛɛn mi sɑ bɛɛ yiire sɑ nɛɛ, wi u kun kĩ u sɔmburu ko, n ǹ mɑɑ weenɛ yɛ̃ro u di.
\p 
\v 11 Wee, sɑ nuɑ mɑ bɛɛn ɡɑbu bɑ sɑ̃ɑ yikurobu be bɑ kun ɡɑru mɔ̀ mɑ n kun mɔ ɡɑri wɔbiɑ wɔribu.
\v 12 Sɑ tɔn ben bweseru yiiremɔ sɑ bu suuru kɑnɑmɔ Yinni Yesu Kirisin sɔ̃, bu de bu sɔmburu ko lɑɑkɑri sɔɔ kpɑ bu ben tii diisiɑ.
\p 
\v 13 Adɑmɑ bɛɛ nɛɡibu, i ku wɑsirɑ kɑ ɡeɑn kobu.
\v 14 Goo ù n yinɑ u ɡɑri yi mɛm nɔɔwɑ yi sɑ yoruɑ tire teni sɔɔ, i n nùn lɑɑkɑri sɑ̃ɑ kpɑ i kun mɑɑ ɡɑ̃ɑnu mɔɔsinɛ kɑ wi, n wɑ sekuru tu nùn mwɑ.
\v 15 I ku nùn ɡɑrisi nɡe yibɛrɛ, ɑdɑmɑ i nùn swɑɑ sɔ̃ɔsio mɛro bisi bisikum.
\s1 Domɑru kɑ tɔbiribu
\p 
\v 16 Yinni wi u rɑ ɑlɑfiɑ wɛ̃ u bɛɛ ɑlɑfiɑ kɛ̃ sɑɑ bɑɑyere ye n bɛɛ deemɑ kpuro sɔɔ kpɑ u n kɑ bɛɛ kpuro wɑ̃ɑ.
\p 
\v 17 Kɑ nɛn tiin nɔmuwɑ nɑ yeni yoruɑ. Nɛ Pɔlu nɑ bɛɛ tɔburɑ. Yerɑ n sɑ̃ɑ nɛn yĩreru nɛn tirenu kpuro sɔɔ.
\p 
\v 18 Nɛn yorɑ mi. Kpɑ bɛsɛn Yinni Yesu Kirisin durom mu n kɑ bɛɛ kpuro wɑ̃ɑ.
